    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-04-29T17:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-04-29T17:00:00-05:00" n="1396"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1396">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The</hi>
                    <gloss type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State</hi>
                    </gloss>
                    <hi rend="italic">to the Ambassador in Turkey</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_MH1"
                        type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morgenthau</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-04-29T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 29, 1915, 5 p. m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>633. Department’s April 27 and your 608, April 27. Urge Turkish Government to
                    protect both Armenians and Zionists.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_BWJ1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
